20company%20pull%20promotions%20for%20its%20Pride%20merch%2C%20comparing%20them%20to%20MAGA%20products.%C2%A0The%20leaked%20message%20sparked%20outrage%20and%20an%20apology%20from%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Matt%20Meeker%2C%20who%20said%20the%20company%20stands%20by%20its%20Pride%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c7366a5-ab3c-4280-a330-0f1576d44db9%5C%22%3ECompanies%20haven't%20had%20the%20best%20time%20sticking%20the%20landing%20with%20Pride%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPride%20Month%2C%20Nolan%20said%2C%20became%20%26quot%3Bmore%20a%20checklist%20of%20corporate%20fears%20than%20it%20was%20a%20checklist%20of%20consumer%20desires.%26quot%3B%20People%20never%20asked%20for%20brands%20to%20add%20rainbows%20to%20their%20logos%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Nolan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20have%20faced%20pressure%20from%20more%20left-wing%20groups%20that%20accused%20them%20of%20%26quot%3Brainbow%20washing%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20capitalizing%20on%20LGBTQ%2B%20people%20without%20providing%20a%20tangible%20benefit%20to%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPride%20Month%20became%20more%20of%20a%20minefield%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20as%20conservatives%20took%20aim%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbud-light-transgender-controversy-backlash-boycotts-history%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBud%20Light's%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20transgender%20influencer%20Dylan%20Mulvaney%2C%20and%20followed%20quickly%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-says-lgbtq-pride-backlash-hurt-sales-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETarget%20facing%20blowback%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%202023%20Pride%20merchandise%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bud%20Light%20and%20Target%20walked%20back%20their%20LGBTQ%2B%20campaigns%2C%20the%20retreats%20didn't%20exactly%20earn%20them%20goodwill%20from%20either%20side%20of%20the%20political%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20division%20between%20the%20sides%20has%20only%20gr