ck%20funds.%20If%20they%20hit%201%25%20of%20their%20current%20assets%20under%20management%20within%20a%20four-week%20span%2C%20the%20sell%20signal%20is%20activated.%20Over%20the%20last%20four%20weeks%2C%20flows%20totaled%200.9%25%20of%20the%20funds'%20AUM.%20To%20hit%201%25%2C%20flows%20would%20have%20to%20hit%20%2430%20billion%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bcoming%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20Hartnett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20a%20breadth%20indicator%20that%20says%20when%2088%25%20of%20the%20ACWI%20countries'%20indexes%20trade%20above%20both%20their%2050-day%20and%20200-day%20moving%20averages%2C%20it's%20a%20sign%20that%20things%20are%20frothy%20and%20investors%20should%20sell%2C%20Hartnett%20said.%20Currently%2C%2084%25%20of%20ACWI%20countries'%20indexes%20are%20higher%20than%20their%20moving%20averages%2C%20meaning%20the%20market%20is%20in%20%26quot%3Boverbought%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20Hartnett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20Hartnett's%20sell%20indicators%20are%20in%20line%20with%20the%20conventional%20wisdom%20of%20contrarian%20investing%20espoused%20by%20legends%20like%20Warren%20Buffett.%20When%20the%20market%20is%20overwhelmingly%20bullish%2C%20good%20news%20is%20already%20priced%20in.%20When%20investors%20are%20bearish%2C%20it's%20an%20opportunity%20to%20buy%20stocks%20at%20a%20discount%2C%20the%20thinking%20goes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20sentiment%20gauges%20have%20sent%20mixed%20signals%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20months.%20While%20inflows%20are%20strong%2C%20the%20AAII%20Investor%20Sentiment%20Survey%20shows%20investors%20are%20still%20net%20bearish.%20Bank%20of%20America's%20own%20Bull%2FBear%20indicator%20shows%20the%20market's%20aggregate%20attitude%20hovers%20somewhere%20between%20optimism%20and%20pessimism%2C%20with%20a%20slight%20tilt%20toward%20the%20former.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreadth%20indicators%20are%20broadly%20in%20line%20with%20Hartnett's%20measure.%20Stocks%20of%20all%20stripes%20are%20doing%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Hart