d%20millet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20joy%20of%20reviving%20lost%20foods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20two%20years%2C%20Gepo%20Aali%20has%20garnered%20around%20150%20loyal%20customers%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%94%20a%20small%20but%20meaningful%20community%20that%20believes%20in%20Dimum%E2%80%99s%20vision.%20While%20revenue%20has%20been%20modest%2C%20reflecting%20the%20challenges%20of%20scaling%20a%20grassroots%20food%20venture%20in%20a%20remote%20region%2C%20Dimum%20remains%20undeterred.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20focus%20has%20never%20been%20on%20rapid%20growth%20or%20profit%20margins.%20Instead%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20rooted%20in%20steady%20and%20sustainable%20impact%20%E2%80%94%20building%20seed%20banks%2C%20empowering%20women%20through%20financial%20models%20like%20ROCA%20(Rotating%20Savings%20and%20Credit%20Association)%2C%20and%20preserving%20indigenous%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20her%20goals%20are%20ambitious%20yet%20deeply%20connected%20with%20community%20care.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20look%20for%20more%20such%20foods%20and%20revive%20them%20effectively%2C%20bring%20them%20to%20our%20seed%20bank%2C%20and%20expand%20our%20women%20workforce.%20%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20aim%20is%20not%20just%20agricultural%20revival%2C%20but%20financial%20inclusion%20%E2%80%94%20giving%20women%20the%20tools%20and%20support%20to%20grow%2C%20earn%2C%20and%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20of%20course%2C%20she%20dreams%20of%20sending%20the%20goodness%20of%20Adlay%20millet%20across%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20year%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20achieve%20pan-India%20shipping%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20quiet%20determination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDimum%20Pertin%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20a%20beautiful%20reminder%20that%20the%20most%20powerful%20innovations%20often%20rise%20from%20humble%20beginnings%20%E2%80%94%20a%20longing%20to%20preserve%20the%20past%20and%20a%20deep%20love%20for%20one%E2%