20I%20thought%20about%20food%20and%20its%20role%20in%20our%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20introduction%20to%20microgreens%20dates%20back%20to%202011%2C%20when%20he%20met%20with%20a%20researcher%20from%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20discussed%20how%20lifestyle%20diseases%20could%20be%20combated%20through%20healthier%20and%20more%20sustainable%20living%2C%20and%20one%20thing%20led%20to%20another.%20We%20started%20discussing%20microgreens%20and%20I%20was%20intrigued%20to%20know%20about%20their%20benefits%2C%20but%20it%20took%20years%20for%20me%20to%20act%20on%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20pharma%20to%20farming%3A%20Only%20to%20grow%20chemical-free%20microgreens%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20seeing%20his%20relatives%20struggle%20with%20health%20problems%2C%20and%20with%20encouragement%20from%20doctors%20who%20spoke%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20chemically-laden%20foods%2C%20the%20former%20corporate%20professional%20made%20a%20radical%20decision.%20In%20December%202020%2C%20he%20resigned%20from%20his%20senior%20position%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%20and%20decided%20to%20restart%20his%20career%20with%20a%20new%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T215254.508_11zon-1749054184.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20May%202022%2C%20Mohit%20founded%20Embryonic%20Greens%20(Opc)%20Private%20Limited%20