explained%20to%20everyone%20the%20benefits%20of%20microgreens%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20business%20started%20to%20grow%20after%20he%20explained%20to%20everyone%20why%20these%20miniature%20vegetables%20are%20nutritious.%20One%20of%20his%20first%20customers%20was%20an%20oncologist%20based%20in%20Chandigarh.%20After%20trying%20the%20microgreens%2C%20he%20became%20a%20vocal%20advocate%20for%20the%20health%20benefits%20of%20these%20tiny%20plants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oncologist%20told%20me%20that%20microgreens%20could%20make%20a%20difference%20not%20only%20for%20his%20patients%20but%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F322864%2Fkochi-aathira-sethumadhavan-pcos-weight-loss-healthy-diet-nutrition-sustainable-lifestyle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanyone%20seeking%20a%20healthier%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20says.%20This%20feedback%20gave%20him%20the%20confidence%20to%20push%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jatin%20Sarin%2C%20a%20senior%20consultant%20in%20oncology%20based%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CCancer%20is%20increasingly%20recognised%20as%20a%20lifestyle%20disease%2C%20with%20poor%20dietary%20habits%20playing%20a%20major%20role.%20Our%20food%20today%20is%20often%20packed%20with%20chemicals%20and%20has%20fewer%20essential%20nutrients.%20Microgreens%2C%20however%2C%20are%20a%20different%20story.%20These%20young%20plants%2C%20which%20are%20harvested%20after%20the%20sprout%20stage%2C%20are%20packed%20with%20micronutrients%20and%20offer%20a%20wealth%20of%20health%20benefits.%20They%20can%20be%20a%20valuable%20addition%20to%20a%20p