ar%2C%20much%20of%20which%20remains%20non-recyclable%20and%20persistent%20in%20the%20environment%20(Source%3A%20UNEP%2C%20CPCB).%20As%20global%20and%20domestic%20regulations%20tighten%20around%20plastic%20use%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20viable%2C%20biodegradable%20alternatives%20is%20not%20only%20growing%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20essential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140040.298-1749033760.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BCML%20team%20along%20with%20the%20CM%20of%20Maharashtra%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140040.298-1749033760.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140040.298-1749033760-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140040.298-1749033760-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140040.298-1749033760-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140040.298-1749033760-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444161%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20brand%20%E2%80%98Balrampur%20Bioyug%E2%80%99%20was%20launched%20on%2027%20May%202025%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20step%20for%20India%20to%20become%20the%20biochemical%20hub.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20Balrampur%20Chini%20Mills%20Limited%20(BCML)%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20integrated%20sugar%20producers%20%E2%80%94%20is%20rewriting%20the%20role%20of%20sugarcane%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20sustainability%20journey.%20With%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20brand%20%E2%80%98Balrampur%20Bioyug%E2%80%99%20on%2027th%20May%202025%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20industrial-scale%20PLA%20(polylactic%20acid)%20biopolymer%20plant%20and%20powered%20by%20renewable%20energy%2C%20which%20will%20be%20commissioned%20in%20October%202026%2C%20BCML%20will%20be%20transforming%20sugar%20from%20sugarcane%20into%20fully%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263744%2Fancient-india-leaf-republic-german-sal-leaves-eco-friendly-pattals-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompostable%2C%20bio-based%20plastic%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20be%20the%20best%20alternative%20to%20the%20banned%20single-use%20plastic%20items%20and%20other%20applications%20across%20industries%20like%20packaging%2C%20bio-medical%2C%20food%20service%20ware%20and%20more.%20Located%20in%20Kumbhi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20this%20initiative%20marks%20a%20critical%20step%20in%20aligning%20agriculture%2C%20industry%2C%20and%20sustainability%20at%20scale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20haven%E2%80%99t%20just%20unveiled%20a%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20we%20launched%20a%20transformative%20movement.%20Bioyug%2C%20symbolising%20%E2%80%98The%20Era%20of%20Bio-Circularity%E2%80%99%2C%20marks%20a%20pivotal%20step%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20transition%20to%20a%20bio-based%2C%20low-carbon%20economy%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Avantika%20Saraogi%2C%20Executive%20Director%20of%20Balrampur%20Chini%20Mills%20Limited%20(BCML)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20a%20staple%20crop%20for%20the%20kitchen%20table%20will%20now%20be%20poised%20to%20become%20a%20building%20block%20for%20the%20packaging%20of%20the%20future%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20biodegrades%20naturally%2C%20reduces%20fossil-fuel%20dependence%2C%20and%20supports%20both%20climate%20goals%20and%20rural%20economies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20a%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20sparked%20a%20bio-revolution%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Avantika%2C%20the%20idea%20didn%E2%80%99t%20begin%20in%20a%20boardroom%20or%20a%20strategy%20document.%20It%20started%20with%20a%20moment%20of%20loss%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20that%20followed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20grandmother%2C%20fondly%20called%20%E2%80%98Madamji%E2%80%99%2C%20passed%20away%2C%20I%20took%20over%20the%20sugarcane%20side%20of%20the%20business%20after%20about%205%20years%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20used%20to%20handle.%20There%20was%20a%20vacuum%2C%20and%20our%20company%20has%20always%20been%20community-knit.%20We%20care%20about%20our%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20because%20of%20their%20blessings%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20do%20everything%20we%20have.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20charge%20of%20a%20part%20of%20the%20company%20so%20closely%20linked%20to%20her%20grandmother%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20managing%20operations.%20It%20became%20a%20personal%20question%3A%20%3Cem%3EWhat%20more%20can%20we%20do%20with%20what%20we%20already%20have%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20Her%20grandmother%20had%20built%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20successful%20sugar%20and%20ethanol%20enterprises%20through%20sheer%20dedication%20%E2%80%94%20staying%20close%20to%20the%20people%2C%20the%20land%2C%20and%20the%20work%20itself.%20Carrying%20that%20forward%20meant%20not%20simply%20continuing%20business%20as%20usual%2C%20but%20asking%20how%20that%20legacy%20could%20take%20on%20new%20meaning%20in%20a%20changing%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20question%20led%20Avantika%20to%20look%20more%20closely%20at%20sugarcane%E2%80%99s%20by-products%20%E2%80%94%20the%20parts%20of%20the%20crop%20often%20overlooked%20once%20the%20juice%20and%20sugar%20are%20extracted.%20One%20day%2C%20she%20came%20across%20a%20bottle%20made%20from%20sugarcane.%20It%20looked%20like%20regular%20plastic%20but%20had%20a%20quiet%20statement%20printed%20on%20it%3A%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20made%20from%20plants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T135912.878-1749033796.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Avantika%20Saraogi%2C%20Executive%20Director%2C%20BCML%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T135912.878-1749033796.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T135912.878-1749033796-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T135912.878-1749033796-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T135912.878-1749033796-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T135912.878-1749033796-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444162%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20young%20woman%E2%80%99s%20dream%20has%20now%20shaped%20the%20goal%20of%20BCML.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20looked%20just%20like%20plastic%2C%20but%20it%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20made%20from%20plants%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20it%20was%20all%20sugarcane.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20idea%20took%20hold.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20spark%20of%20curiosity%20soon%20became%20a%20possibility%20worth%20pursuing.%20If%20sugarcane%20could%20be%20used%20to%20make%20packaging%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pollute%20the%20earth%2C%20what%20would%20it%20take%20to%20bring%20that%20to%20India%2C%20at%20scale%20and%20from%20within%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20question%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20stay%20with%20her.%20It%20began%20to%20grow%20inside%20the%20company.%20Slowly%2C%20it%20made%20its%20way%20into%20conversations%2C%20plans%2C%20and%20deeper%20research.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20reason%20that%20the%20senior%20leadership%20team%20and%20the%20board%20said%20yes%20is%20that%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20say%20no%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20Avantika%20says.%20%E2%80%9CLiterally%20every%20question%20had%20a%20very%20good%20answer%20and%20a%20perfect%20business%20case.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Bio%E2%80%99%20reflects%20our%20commitment%20to%20sustainable%2C%20plant-based%20materials%20like%20PLA%20and%20our%20integration%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20agri-value%20chain%2C%20especially%20sugarcane%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20%E2%80%98Yug%E2%80%99%2C%20from%20Sanskrit%2C%20signifies%20a%20new%20era%20built%20on%20ecological%20responsibility%20and%20circularity%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Avantika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20that%20seed%20of%20an%20idea%20has%20taken%20shape%20as%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20brand%20Balrampur%20Bioyug%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20industrial-scale%20PLA%20(polylactic%20acid)%20biopolymer%20plant%2C%20which%20will%20be%20converting%20sugar%20into%20a%20plastic%20alternative%20designed%20to%20return%20to%20the%20earth.%20But%20its%20real%20origin%20lies%20in%20something%20far%20simpler%20and%20more%20enduring%3A%20a%20woman%20at%20the%20helm%20asking%20what%20more%20was%20possible%20with%20what%20her%20family%20had%20built%20and%20how%20it%20could%20mean%20more%20for%20the%20people%20they%20serve%20and%20the%20world%20they%20share.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20core%20philosophy%20of%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98more%20from%20less%E2%80%99%20was%20deeply%20reinforced%20by%20my%20father%2C%20Mr.%20Vivek%20Saraogi%2C%20whose%20leadership%20has%20driven%20the%20digital%20transformation%20of%20our%20operations%20and%20guided%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20diversification%20into%20the%20distillery%20and%20cogen%20segments%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Avantika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20crop%20to%20compostable%3A%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20end-to-end%20PLA%20plant%20powered%20by%20agriculture%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20PLA%20plants%2C%20BCML%E2%80%99s%20facility%20will%20be%20fully%20integrated.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20functioning%2C%20this%20will%20be%20the%20first%20plant%20globally%20to%20go%20from%20sugarcane%20to%20PLA%20in%20one%20location%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Avantika.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20it%20will%20also%20be%20the%20first%20PLA%20plant%20powered%20completely%20by%20renewable%20energy%2C%20either%20from%20bagasse%20or%20other%20agricultural%20waste.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20big%20bet.%20But%20BCML%20isn%E2%80%99t%20new%20to%20pioneering.%20With%20ten%20sugar%20units%2C%20five%20distilleries%2C%20and%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20robust%20ethanol%20production%20networks%2C%20the%20company%20has%20always%20moved%20with%20foresight.%20The%20addition%20of%20bioplastics%20is%20a%20natural%20next%20step.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20inevitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Avantika%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CSugarcane-based%20industry%20is%20sort%20of%20like%20an%20oil%20rig.%20Until%20now%2C%20only%20the%20oil%20industry%20has%20made%20plastic.%20Now%2C%20sugarcane-based%20industries%20can%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%2C%20creating%20new%20paths%20for%20other%20sugar%20producers%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20sugarcane%20becomes%20plastic%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurning%20sugarcane%20into%20plastic%20may%20sound%20like%20science%20fiction%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20science%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20remarkably%20efficient%20one.%20With%20the%20right%20processes%20and%20the%20right%20intent%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20traditional%20crops%20can%20become%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20sustainable%20material%20revolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20simple%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3Cstrong%3EStefan%20Barot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20President%20of%20the%20Chemical%20Division%20at%20Balrampur%20Chini%20Mills.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20start%20with%20sugar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20natural%2C%20fairly%20well-defined%20raw%20material.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20pure%20like%20chemicals%2C%20of%20course%3B%20it%20has%20some%20impurities.%20But%20nature%20has%20already%20done%20half%20the%20work.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20exactly%20does%20sugar%20become%20something%20that%20looks%20and%20acts%20like%20plastic%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20break%20it%20down%20step%20by%20step%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFermentation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20sugar%2C%20taken%20from%20sugarcane%20juice%2C%20is%20fermented%2C%20like%20how%20you%20make%20curd%20or%20wine.%20This%20process%20produces%20%3Cstrong%3Elactic%20acid%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20If%20that%20sounds%20familiar%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20because%20your%20body%20makes%20lactic%20acid%20when%20your%20muscles%20are%20tired%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20found%20in%20compost%20heaps.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20natural%20and%20already%20part%20of%20our%20everyday%20lives.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurification%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Next%2C%20this%20lactic%20acid%20is%20cleaned%20up.%20It%20goes%20through%20a%20purification%20process%20that%20removes%20impurities%2C%20but%20importantly%2C%20this%20is%20done%20without%20using%20any%20harsh%20or%20harmful%20chemicals.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20clean%20process%20that%20keeps%20the%20material%20safe%20and%20sustainable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimerisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Water%20is%20removed%20from%20the%20lactic%20acid%20to%20make%20something%20called%20a%20%3Cstrong%3Edimer%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20You%20can%20think%20of%20this%20as%20getting%20the%20molecules%20to%20link%20together%2C%20like%20prepping%20puzzle%20pieces%20so%20they%20snap%20into%20place.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolymerisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20In%20the%20final%20step%2C%20these%20dimers%20are%20connected%20into%20long%20chains%2C%20forming%20what%E2%80%99s%20called%20%3Cstrong%3EPLA%20resin%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20This%20material%20can%20be%20shaped%20into%20bottles%2C%20containers%2C%20utensils%2C%20and%20other%20packaging%20products%E2%80%94things%20we%20typically%20use%20plastic%20for.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20difference%3F%20%3Cstrong%3EPLA%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stick%20around%20forever.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20traditional%20plastic%2C%20which%20can%20last%20hundreds%20of%20years%2C%20PLA%20is%20designed%20to%20break%20down.%20In%20industrial%20composting%20facilities%2C%20where%20there%E2%80%99s%20heat%2C%20moisture%2C%20and%20the%20right%20microbes%2C%20it%20decomposes%20quickly%20and%20turns%20back%20into%20compost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20these%20conditions%2C%20PLA%20goes%20away%20in%20just%20180%20days.%20In%20reality%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F406959%2Fseaweed-plastic-packaging-alternatives-india-startups%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20normally%20goes%20away%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Stefan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20India%20moves%20away%20from%20single-use%20plastics%2C%20materials%20like%20PLA%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20tick%20the%20sustainability%20box%20%E2%80%94%20they%20offer%20a%20real%2C%20working%20alternative%20that%20can%20be%20scaled%20and%20used%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%C2%A0But%20why%20sugarcane%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Stefan%2C%20it%20comes%20down%20to%20efficiency%20and%20yield.%20%E2%80%9CSugarcane%20gives%20you%20a%20denser%2C%20more%20efficient%20yield.%20You%20get%20about%2011%E2%80%9312%25%20of%20sugar%20out%20of%20sugarcane.%20Corn%20just%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20compare%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20much%20sugar%20you%20can%20extract%20per%20square%20metre%20of%20land.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20only%20one%20crop%20with%20a%20better%20sugar%20yield%3A%20sugar%20beet%2C%20which%20grows%20seasonally%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20flourish%20in%20Indian%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20makes%20sugarcane%20the%20ideal%20raw%20material%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20bioplastic%20revolution.%20It%E2%80%99s%20abundant%2C%20renewable%2C%20and%20already%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20our%20agricultural%20landscape.%20Plus%2C%20it%20grows%20year-round%2C%20supports%20millions%20of%20farmers%2C%20and%20now%2C%20thanks%20to%20BCML%2C%20can%20even%20power%20a%20shift%20towards%20a%20circular%2C%20bio-based%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20renewables%20power%20the%20plant%2C%20BCML%E2%80%99s%20PLA%2C%20once%20it%E2%80%99s%20up%20and%20running%2C%20could%20achieve%20up%20to%2080%25%20lower%20carbon%20footprint%20than%20traditional%20plastics%20like%20PET.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20be%20bio-based%20plastic%20made%20by%20bio-based%20energy.%20Everything%20comes%20from%20the%20earth%20and%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20earth%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Avantika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFarmers%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20story%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20sets%20Balrampur%20Bioyug%20apart%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20its%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20people%20behind%20it.%20For%20the%205.5%20lakh%20farmers%20associated%20with%20BCML%2C%20it%20goes%20beyond%20another%20industrial%20facility%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20symbol%20of%20shared%20purpose%2C%20where%20agriculture%20meets%20global%20innovation.%20It%20puts%20farmers%20not%20at%20the%20periphery%20of%20progress%2C%20but%20at%20its%20very%20centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20farmers%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20plant.%20Without%20their%20sugarcane%2C%20this%20facility%20is%20just%20metal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3Cstrong%3EAvantika%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20spoke%20to%20them%20about%20bioplastics%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20much%20about%20plastic%20or%20composting.%20But%20now%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20proud%20to%20say%20that%20they%20will%20grow%20for%20a%20bioplastic%20plant.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140407.335-1749033850.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22farmer%20working%20in%20the%20sugarcane%20field%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140407.335-1749033850.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140407.335-1749033850-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140407.335-1749033850-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140407.335-1749033850-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140407.335-1749033850-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444164%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBalrampur%20Bioyug%20would%